PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?club ?clubLabel WHERE {
  ?club wdt:P31 wd:Q476028 .
  ?club wdt:P131 ?location .
  ?location wdt:P131 * wd:Q29 .
  ?club rdfs:label ?clubLabel .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?clubLabel ) = "en" )
}

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?country ?countryLabel ( COUNT( ?language ) AS ?languageCount ) WHERE {
  ?country wdt:P31 wd:Q6256 .
  ?country wdt:P37 ?language .
  OPTIONAL {
    ?country rdfs:label ?countryLabel FILTER ( LANG( ?countryLabel ) = "en" )
  }
}
GROUP BY ?country ?countryLabel
HAVING ( COUNT( ?language ) > 2 )
ORDER BY DESC ( ?languageCount )
LIMIT 100

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?country ?countryLabel WHERE {
  wd:Q78707 wdt:P131 ?adminEntity .
  ?adminEntity wdt:P17 ?country .
  ?country rdfs:label ?countryLabel .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?countryLabel ) = "en" )
}

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?country WHERE {
  ?country wdt:P31 wd:Q6256 .
  ?country wdt:P122 ?govType .
  FILTER ( ?govType IN ( wd:Q117405807 , wd:Q50686 , wd:Q842112 ) )
}

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?country WHERE {
  ?cave wdt:P31 / wdt:P279 * wd:Q35509 .
  ?cave wdt:P131 ?adminEntity .
  ?adminEntity wdt:P17 ?country .
}
GROUP BY ?country
HAVING ( COUNT( ?cave ) > 10 )
ORDER BY DESC ( COUNT( ?cave ) )

PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
SELECT ?date WHERE {
  wd:Q211 p:P463 ?statement .
  ?statement ps:P463 wd:Q458 ; pq:P580 ?date .
}
